snippet.title: Children of Zodiarcs July 18, 2017!!!!
snippet.description: Yup! Children of Zodiarcs, the single-player deck and dice tactical RPG, is releasing on PlayStation 4 and Steam (Windows) this July 18, 2017!!! You can wishlist the game on Steam now! http://store.steampowered.com/app/436290/Children_of_Zodiarcs/
